3.6 Login by Checker:  
a. Approve/Reject BC & OR plan  
Step 1: Click on â€œ+Planâ€ and then â€œPending as Branch Checkerâ€. Checker can view all the details and provide approval if the Plan is in 
order. In case of any discrepancies the plan may be rejected by the Checker. All 7 parts need to be verified before approving or rejecting.   
23  
Step 2: After verifying, the checker needs to approve or reject the plan. Rejecting the plan by Checker will put the plan on the tray of 
Maker. The checker can put comments stating the reason for rejecting the proposal. Approving the plan leads to submission of the plan 
to Alternate Branch/Office Checker. Once rejected, it will be shown as draft in the Maker tab.  
